context_meta.summary: The population of Hawkins, Ind., will grow by at least one person when Stranger Things returns for Season 3. The streaming service, making early casting announcements for the new edition, also has promoted Priah Ferguson, who plays Lucas's little sister, Erica Sinclair, to recurring status on the popular horror drama. Hawke, the daughter of Uma Thurman and Ethan Hawke, will play Robin, described as "an alternative girl who is equal parts sharp and playful.
